1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to appropriations; to appropriate funds to aid
2 in carrying out the provisions of Legislative Bill 1165, One Hundred
3 Ninth Legislature, Second Session, 2026; and to declare an
4 emergency.
5 Be it enacted by the people of the State of Nebraska,
-1-

LB1165A LB1165A
2026 2026
1 Section 1. There is hereby appropriated (1) $2,000,000 from the
2 Site and Building Development Fund for FY2026-27 and (2) $-0- from the
3 Site and Building Development Fund for FY2027-28 to the Department of
4 Economic Development, for Program 603, to aid in carrying out the
5 provisions of Legislative Bill 1165, One Hundred Ninth Legislature,
6 Second Session, 2026.
7 There is included in the appropriation to this program for FY2026-27
8 $2,000,000 Cash Funds for state aid, which shall only be used for such
9 purpose. There is included in the appropriation to this program for
10 FY2027-28 $-0- Cash Funds for state aid, which shall only be used for
11 such purpose.
12 No expenditures for permanent and temporary salaries and per diems
13 for state employees shall be made from funds appropriated in this
14 section.
15 Sec. 2. Since an emergency exists, this act takes effect when
16 passed and approved according to law.
